programme.title: Akibat Jadi Istri Kedua Yang Tamak

programme.title: Cewek Keling

programme.title: Cewek Keling

programme.title: Toko Kr.Amat : Gaun Biduan Dangdut
programme.desc: Titin bercita-cita menjadi pedangdut terkenal, tapi wajahnya tidak cantik. Di toko KR Amat, dia menemukan gaun yang bisa membuatnya terkenal.

programme.title: Toko Kr.Amat : Gaun Biduan Dangdut

programme.title: Cinta DP 0 Persen

programme.title: Sweet 16

programme.title: Sweet 16

programme.title: Ada Apanya Dengan Cinta?
programme.desc: Mita adalah gadis cantik yang manja. Suatu hari, dia bertemu dengan Rasta, pemuda berpenampilan dekil tapi memiliki sorot mata yang tulus dan hangat.

programme.title: Ada Apanya Dengan Cinta?
programme.desc: Mita is a pretty and spoiled girl. One day, she meets Rasta, a man who looks shabby but with strong and sincere gaze.

programme.title: Kids Gaul Jaman Now
programme.desc: Saat masih muda, kita selalu mencari kesenangan dan kebahagiaan sambil melalui hal-hal yang membingungkan: begitulah masa muda.

programme.title: Kids Gaul Jaman Now
programme.desc: When we were young, we're always looking for pleasure and happiness, while navigating the confusing parts in our lives: such is youth.

programme.title: Mencuri Patung Merlion
programme.desc: Tania baru pulang dari Singapura dan dia berfoto di depan patung merlion. Risa ditantang untuk mengambil patung merlion. Dengan penuh semangat Risa bekerja keras dan akhirnya dia berangkat ke Singapura dan pulang membawa cokelat berbentuk Merlion.

programme.title: Mencuri Patung Merlion
programme.desc: Tania had just returned from Singapore and she took pictures in front of the Merlion statue. Risa was challenged to take a Merlion statue, so she worked hard and eventually she managed to go to Singapore and return with Merlion-shaped Chocolates.

programme.title: Pamali: Jangan Tinggal Di Rumah Tusuk Sate
programme.desc: Satu pasangan yang baru menikah membeli sebuah rumah tua. Namun ternyata rumah yang baru mereka beli tersebut berada di posisi tusuk sate. Konon menurut cerita orang-orang, mereka akan mengalami banyak kesialan dalam hidup.

programme.title: Pamali: Jangan Tinggal Di Rumah Tusuk Sate
programme.desc: A newly wed bought an old house. However, their newly purchased home turned out to be located in a three-junction road corner. According to the people around their house, rumours said that they would get many misfortunes in their life.

programme.title: Aroma Cinta Isi Ulang
programme.desc: Saat sedang mengikuti pacarnya yang dia curigai berselingkuh, Indri terpaksa menebeng mobil pikap pembawa sampah. Dia pun terpaksa mampir ke toko parfum untuk menghilangkan baunya, sayangnya penjualnya adalah pria menyebalkan.

programme.title: Aroma Cinta Isi Ulang
programme.desc: When following her boyfriend whom she suspected is cheating on her, Indri was forced to hitch a ride in a trash pickup truck. She then went to a perfumery to buy a perfume to erase the smell, but unfortunately, the seller is an annoying man.

programme.title: Komisi Pemberantas Setan 3

programme.title: Komisi Pemberantas Setan 3
programme.desc: Burhan is a 17 year old high school student who joined the group KPS aka Satan Eradication Commission. He has the special gift. He is able to see ghosts and spirits around him, such gift that passed down in his family for generations.

programme.title: Pancing Ikan Cinta Kutangkap

programme.title: Pancing Ikan Cinta Kutangkap

programme.title: Asmara Segede Bakpao

programme.title: Asmara Segede Bakpao

programme.title: Antara Cinta Dan Pizza

programme.title: Antara Cinta Dan Pizza

programme.title: Mantan's Wedding Bikin Keki

programme.title: Jaka Kendil Mencari Cinta

programme.title: Tengkulak Beras Yang Curang

programme.title: Tengkulak Beras Yang Curang

programme.title: Koran Terakhir Di Kampung Rambutan

programme.title: Akibat Perjanjian Maut Dengan Nyai Ronggeng
programme.desc: Di ulang tahun pernikahan yang ke-7, Adam dan Saraz belum juga mendapatkan keturunan. Setelah melakukan perjanjian dengan Nyai Ronggeng, mereka dikarunia seorang putri. Namun, karena lupa memberikan sesajen, Adam dan Saraz mendapatkan malapetaka.

programme.title: Akibat Perjanjian Maut Dengan Nyai Ronggeng
programme.desc: On their 7th wedding anniversary, Adam and Saraz have not children yet. After making an agreement with Nyai Ronggeng, they are blessed with a daughter. However, Adam and Saraz forget to give offerings that lead them to get into disaster.

programme.title: Baju Orange Jangan Sampai Lolos

programme.title: Baju Orange Jangan Sampai Lolos
programme.desc: Bara is a master's student who is rich, admirable, and already has a girlfriend. His life seems to be going smoothly until one day he meets a garbage cleaning girl who slaps him with reality.

programme.title: Ujian Cinta 16 Hari
programme.desc: Tedy adalah playboy yang gemar balapan liar. Suatu hari, dia ketahuan selingkuh. Tanpa dia ketahui, sesosok rivalnya di arena ternyata mengenal mantan-mantan pacarnya.

programme.title: Ujian Cinta 16 Hari
programme.desc: Tedy is a womanizer who loves street racing. One day, he got caught cheating. Unknowingly, his rival on the arena knows those exes of him.

programme.title: Pemuja Mantan
programme.desc: Andien dan Yoga sama-sama baru kehilangan kekasih hati mereka. Hati mereka pun sembuh ketika mereka saling bertemu akibat campur tangan entitas tak terlihat.

programme.title: Pemuja Mantan
programme.desc: Andien and Yoga just lost their lovers. They unexpectedly healed each other after they met with the help of some unseen entities.

programme.title: Ada Rupa Ada Harga
programme.desc: Adel, Lika, dan Elia adalah tiga bersaudari yang cantik dan anggun, tapi dibesarkan dengan cara ala militer oleh ayah mereka. Inilah kisah ketiganya dalam menghadapi hidup dan asmara.

programme.title: Ada Rupa Ada Harga
programme.desc: Adel, Lika, and Elia are beautiful and graceful sisters, but they were raised in military style by their father. This is their stories in living their daily lives and love.

programme.title: Perempuan Bahulaweyan
programme.desc: Rasti telah tiga kali menikah dan suaminya selalu meninggal dunia. Seorang pria religius melihat bahwa Rasti dijaga sesosok makhluk gaib sejak kecil. Berhasilkah mereka berdua mengusir makhluk gaib tersebut dari tubuh Rasti?

programme.title: Perempuan Bahulaweyan
programme.desc: Rasti is a three times widow. all three of her husband had passed away. A religious man finds out that a supernatural creature guards Rasti since her childhood. Will both of them be able to repel the supernatural creature from her?

programme.title: Pamali: Jangan Potong Kuku Malam Hari
programme.desc: Tiga mahasiswa ingin meliput kematian temannya di Gunung Sumbing karena dibunuh oleh hantu perempuan. Karena tidak mengindahkan larangan memotong kuku di malam hari, salah satu dari mereka diculik oleh hantu berbaju merah. Bagaimana kisah selanjutnya?

programme.title: Pamali: Jangan Potong Kuku Malam Hari
programme.desc: Three college students want to cover his friend's death in Mount Sumbing after being killed by a female ghost. For not heeding the prohibition to cut the nails at night, one of them is kidnapped by a red dressed ghost. How will the story unfold?

programme.title: Ketika Hantu Fall In Love
programme.desc: Laura yang baru saja dilamar justru memergoki tunangannya selingkuh. Dikuasai emosi, dia langsung berlari, tapi naasnya dia mengalami kecelakaan. Tiba-tiba dia tersadar, tapi segalanya menjadi aneh.

programme.title: Ketika Hantu Fall In Love
programme.desc: Laura who just got proposed caught the so called fiance cheated on her. Consumed by anger, she ran away, and got hit by a speeding car. When she came to, everything became so weird.

programme.title: Kuli Cinta
programme.desc: Daniel adalah mahasiswa semester akhir yang khawatir tidak bisa lulus tepat waktu. Saat terlambat ke kampus, dia nyaris tertabrak mobil. Dia pun makin cemas saat kesialan terus terjadi setelahnya.

programme.title: Kuli Cinta
programme.desc: Daniel is a senior student at uni who is worried about graduating on time. When he was late to attend class, he was almost hit by a car. His anxiety spiked up when unfortunate events began to occur afterwards.

programme.title: Makhluk Manis Di Kost'an Depan
programme.desc: Sissy bermimpi buruk didatangi hantu yang memperingatkan agar dia tidak dekat dengan Bimo, pria yang tinggal di seberang kosannya. Sementara itu, Bimo tinggal di sana karena naksir Sissy. Bagaimana kelanjutan kisah mereka?

programme.title: Makhluk Manis Di Kost'an Depan
programme.desc: Sissy had a dream where a ghost came to warn her not to be close to Bimo, the man who lives in the dormitory in front of hers. Meanwhile, Bimo lives there because she likes Sissy. What would happen to them then?

programme.title: Cinta DP 0 Persen
programme.desc: Inilah kisah dua insan dari latar belakang yang berbeda: Nino, seorang agen sales real estate dengan Sheila, agen sales sepatu yang jago bela diri.

programme.title: Cinta DP 0 Persen
programme.desc: This is the story of two people from different backgrounds: Nino, a real estate sales agent and Sheila, a shoe sales agent who is good at martial arts.

programme.title: Teror Debt Collector Cantik
programme.desc: Alan adalah pria yang hobi balap motor. Suatu hari, dia bertemu dengan Delia, debt collector yang tidak tegaan tapi punya trauma dengan lelaki.

programme.title: Teror Debt Collector Cantik
programme.desc: Alan is a man who loves bike racing. One day, he met a girl named Delia, a debt collector who wears her heart on her sleeve but also a past trauma with men.

programme.title: Delivery Paket Cinta
programme.desc: Denis adalah mahasiswa tampan yang terkenal di kampusnya. Namun, dia menyimpan satu rahasia, yaitu dia sebenarnya bekerja sebagai kurir pengantar kue.

programme.title: Delivery Paket Cinta
programme.desc: Denis is a handsome and famous chap in the campus. But actually, he has a secret: he actually works as a courier who delivers cakes.

programme.title: Kupinang Kau Di Ranah Minang

programme.title: Kupinang Kau Di Ranah Minang
programme.desc: Raka and Ainun have been in a long distance relationship for several years. This time, Raka has decided to marry Ainun. However, Raka's mother does not approve their relationship and tries to set him up with a wealthy woman.

programme.title: Toko Kr.Amat : Congklak Tua Pengasih
programme.desc: Ratih, seorang yatim piatu, tinggal bersama bibi dan sepupunya yang jahat. Suatu hari, dia bertemu seorang pria berpakaian serba hitam yang memberinya congklak misterius. Perlahan, congklak itu mengubah perilakunya menjadi buruk.

programme.title: Toko Kr.Amat : Congklak Tua Pengasih
programme.desc: Ratih, an orphan, lives with her mean aunt and cousin. One day, she met a man in black who gave her a mysterious congklak, a kind of mancala game. Slowly, the game changes her behavior for the worse.

programme.title: Hijab Yang Tertukar
programme.desc: Kiara terjebak dalam situasi yang mengharuskan ia berpura-pura menjadi Anisa, seorang perempuan yang dijodohkan dengan Fachri. Saat Annisa asli datang, Fachri pun kesulitan untuk memilih antara Kiara atau Anisa.

programme.title: Hijab Yang Tertukar
programme.desc: Kiara is caught in trouble which requires her to pretend to be Anisa, a woman who is betrothed to Fachri. When the real Anisa appeared, Fachri has a difficult time to choose between Kiara or Anisa.

programme.title: Komisi Pemberantas Setan 3

programme.title: Cinta Ketoprak Setan
programme.desc: Donna and Andre are two people with different personalities. From outside, it seems impossible for them to be close to each other, but one day there's one thing that unite these two polar opposites.

programme.title: Cintaku Sampai Di 16

programme.title: Antara Cinta Dan Pizza

programme.title: Terang Kasih

programme.title: Unik Enak

programme.title: Top Trending

programme.title: STB - Sangat Tidak Biasa
programme.desc: This program presents a compilation of information on various issues and topics that will be discussed from various sides and presented by the voiceover.

programme.title: Kumprank

programme.title: Mina Mila

programme.title: Mina Mila

programme.title: Omar & Hana

programme.title: Omar & Hana

programme.title: Lensa Indonesia Pagi

programme.title: Lensa Indonesia Pagi

programme.title: Riko The Series

programme.title: Riko The Series
programme.desc: Eight-year-old Riko is a smart, diligent and active child. His daily life becomes an adventure for Riko and his best friend, Q110 to discover and learn the things around him.

programme.title: Ibra Berkisah

programme.title: Ibra Berkisah
programme.desc: Ibrahim or Ibra is a well-mannered boarding school student who always invites his friends to emulate the Prophet Muhammad, and has lived in a boarding school since he was a child.

programme.title: Santri Boy

programme.title: Adit Sopo Jarwo

programme.title: Adit Sopo Jarwo

programme.desc: Rangga berhasil memperoleh rekaman CCTV yang berisi bukti-bukti penting terkait pembunuhan Ibu Ratih. Penemuan ini menjadi kunci untuk mengungkap kebenaran di balik kejahatan yang telah terjadi.

programme.title: Cinta Yasmin
programme.desc: In a thrilling development, Rangga managed to obtain CCTV footage that contained important evidence related to the murder of Mrs. Ratih. This discovery is the key to uncovering the truth behind the crime that had occurred.

programme.title: Cinta Berakhir Bahagia
programme.desc: Adisty merupakan gadis yang menjadi tulang punggung keluarga untuk melunasi utang keluarganya. Kehidupan yang berat harus dilalui Adisty demi membiayai hidupnya dan keluarga. Ia lalu dipertemukan dengan Pasha, laki-laki terhormat dari keluarga kaya raya.

programme.title: Cinta Berakhir Bahagia
programme.desc: Adisty is a girl who is the backbone of the family to pay off her family's debts. Adisty has to go through a hard life to support her life and that of her family. She then met Pasha, a respectable man from a very rich family.

programme.title: Semua Indah Karena Cinta
programme.desc: Aviv dan Bella adalah sepasang sahabat sejak kecil. Beranjak dewasa, Aviv dan Bella saling jatuh cinta. Bagaimana perjuangan cinta Bella dan Aviv selanjutnya?

programme.title: Semua Indah Karena Cinta
programme.desc: Aviv and Bella are a pair of best friends since childhood. Growing up, Aviv and Bella fall in love with each other. How will Bella and Aviv's love struggle continue?
